// All in one hotkey
// Use dem poppers
// Instructions: Create counter for pouches in
// Razor named Pouch
// Script will recognize up to 8 pouches in bag
// More than 8 and script will not work

useonce

wait 400

// If poppers not loaded in list/untrapped

